<lb n="0191b21" ed="J"/><item xml:id="itemJ33p0191b2101"><note n="0191b2101" resp="CBETA" type="add">［－］【CB】，一【嘉興】</note><app n="0191b2101"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】"><space quantity="0"/></lem><rdg wit="【嘉興】">一</rdg></app>無事出外間行，罰銀一錢。</item>
<lb n="0191b22" ed="J"/><item xml:id="itemJ33p0191b2201"><note n="0191b2201" resp="CBETA" type="add">［－］【CB】，一【嘉興】</note><app n="0191b2201"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】"><space quantity="0"/></lem><rdg wit="【嘉興】">一</rdg></app>侵剋信施者，一罰十。</item>
<lb n="0191b23" ed="J"/><item xml:id="itemJ33p0191b2301"><note n="0191b2301" resp="CBETA" type="add">［－］【CB】，一【嘉興】</note><app n="0191b2301"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】"><space quantity="0"/></lem><rdg wit="【嘉興】">一</rdg></app>二人同行，方可人家宿。獨身宿者，罰銀五錢。</item>
<lb n="0191b24" ed="J"/><item xml:id="itemJ33p0191b2401"><note n="0191b2401" resp="CBETA" type="add">［－］【CB】，一【嘉興】</note><app n="0191b2401"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】"><space quantity="0"/></lem><rdg wit="【嘉興】">一</rdg></app>普陀、天台等遠遊，及湖船聚集婦女處入會，罰
<lb n="0191b25" ed="J"/>銀五錢。</item>
<lb n="0191b26" ed="J"/><item xml:id="itemJ33p0191b2601"><note n="0191b2601" resp="CBETA" type="add">［－］【CB】，一【嘉興】</note><app n="0191b2601"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】"><space quantity="0"/></lem><rdg wit="【嘉興】">一</rdg></app>彼此鬥爭者，各先罰銀三分，後辯曲直。</item>
<lb n="0191b27" ed="J"/><item xml:id="itemJ33p0191b2701"><note n="0191b2701" resp="CBETA" type="add">［－］【CB】，一【嘉興】</note><app n="0191b2701"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】"><space quantity="0"/></lem><rdg wit="【嘉興】">一</rdg></app>故留遠方尼僧住者，罰銀五錢。</item>
<lb n="0191b28" ed="J"/><item xml:id="itemJ33p0191b2801"><note n="0191b2801" resp="CBETA" type="add">［－］【CB】，一【嘉興】</note><app n="0191b2801"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】"><space quantity="0"/></lem><rdg wit="【嘉興】">一</rdg></app>私取常住物者，一罰十。</item>
<lb n="0191b29" ed="J"/><item xml:id="itemJ33p0191b2901"><note n="0191b2901" resp="CBETA" type="add">［－］【CB】，一【嘉興】</note><app n="0191b2901"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】"><space quantity="0"/></lem><rdg wit="【嘉興】">一</rdg></app>招接算命相面收驚等諸婆者，罰銀一錢。</item>
<lb n="0191b30" ed="J"/><item xml:id="itemJ33p0191b3001"><note n="0191b3001" resp="CBETA" type="add">［－］【CB】，一【嘉興】</note><app n="0191b3001"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】"><space quantity="0"/></lem><rdg wit="【嘉興】">一</rdg></app>輕易留人出家者，罰銀五兩，出院。</item>
<pb n="0191c" ed="J" xml:id="J33.B277.0191c"/>
<lb n="0191c01" ed="J"/><item xml:id="itemJ33p0191c0101"><note n="0191c0101" resp="CBETA" type="add">［－］【CB】，一【嘉興】</note><app n="0191c0101"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】"><space quantity="0"/></lem><rdg wit="【嘉興】">一</rdg></app>在庵嫁送有法名女子者，罰銀五兩，出院。</item>
<lb n="0191c02" ed="J"/><item xml:id="itemJ33p0191c0201"><note n="0191c0201" resp="CBETA" type="add">［－］【CB】，一【嘉興】</note><app n="0191c0201"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】"><space quantity="0"/></lem><rdg wit="【嘉興】">一</rdg></app>畜養幼男至十五六歲不發遣者，罰銀三兩。</item>
<lb n="0191c03" ed="J"/><item xml:id="itemJ33p0191c0301"><note n="0191c0301" resp="CBETA" type="add">［－］【CB】，一【嘉興】</note><app n="0191c0301"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】"><space quantity="0"/></lem><rdg wit="【嘉興】">一</rdg></app>以葷腥入庵者，罰銀三兩。</item>
