<lb n="0191c06" ed="J"/><item xml:id="itemJ33p0191c0601"><note n="0191c0601" resp="CBETA" type="add">［－］【CB】，一【嘉興】</note><app n="0191c0601"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】"><space quantity="0"/></lem><rdg wit="【嘉興】">一</rdg></app>擅留在家婦女，為家間口面不和而來者，不勸
